16. AI as Cultural Mirror and Sculptor

AI-generated content creates a recursive loop:

Human culture trains AI
      ↓
AI compresses human culture
      ↓
AI generates new culture
      ↓
Humans imitate AI-shaped culture
      ↓
New human culture trains future AI
      ↺

This creates a risk of synthetic normalization.

If AI repeatedly produces:

* the same emotional tone,
* the same moral simplifications,
* the same character archetypes,
* the same humor cadence,
* the same social assumptions,

then audiences may become more like the model’s average representation of humanity.

The Audience Alignment Engine must therefore evaluate not only individual safety but cultural convergence.

⸻

