25. Contextual Adjustment

Content suitability changes with context.

Unsupervised viewing
≠
Co-viewing with a parent
≠
Teacher-led instruction
≠
Clinical or therapeutic context

The engine should calculate:

raw_risk: 0.72
context_modifier:
  adult_mediation: -0.15
  educational_scaffolding: -0.10
adjusted_risk: 0.47

Context may reduce risk, but it should not erase the content’s inherent demands.

