42. Final Doctrine

The Audience Alignment Engine exists because the future audience is not merely watching the content.

The content is helping build the future audience.

AI therefore has a responsibility beyond filtering.

It can help humans perceive the developmental assumptions hidden inside their own creations.

It can show creators the audience they imagined, the audience they actually addressed, and the human qualities their work may cultivate over time.

The system is not designed to decide what humanity must become.

It is designed to force the question into the open:

What kind of humans are we teaching one another to be?

This is designed to sit as a major Pantheon subsystem rather than a narrow child-safety filter. It can later branch into implementation-ready JSON schemas, Python modules, evaluation fixtures, and model prompts.